## Build

```bash
xcodebuild -project Jot.xcodeproj -scheme Jot -configuration Debug build
```

Do NOT relaunch after building ‚Äî user handles relaunch via in-app updates panel.

## Key Architectural Decisions

- `NSColor.labelColor` everywhere ‚Äî no hardcoded dark/light RGB tuples
- `styleTodoParagraphs()` skips heading paragraphs via `headingLevel(for:)` guard
- `fixInconsistentFonts()` skips heading fonts (Writing Tools must not downgrade them)
- `TextFormattingManager` methods accept `NSTextView` (not `NSTextStorage`) for undo support
- Editor blocks (code/callout/tabs/file previews) use `NSTextAttachment` + `NSView` overlay pattern
- File preview overlays use synchronous `updateFilePreviewOverlays` (not async `scheduleOverlayUpdate`)
- `NSHostingView` overlays must receive `containerWidth` BEFORE `rebuildHostingView()` runs
- Metadata panels (AI/meeting) are SwiftUI views in `NoteDetailView` VStack
- Properties panel: always-present in `HStack` (width 0‚Üî340), no conditional insertion; uses `propertiesPanelSlot()` in `ContentView`
- UI zoom uses `GeometryReader` + `scaleEffect` + counter-scaled frame in `JotApp.swift`
- Meeting sessions stored as `[MeetingSession]` (JSON-encoded Data on `NoteEntity`)
- AI summary pipeline uses `NLTokenizer` chunking + grounding validation
- Quick Look hover uses `QLPreviewPanel` (not `NSWorkspace`) ‚Äî images use separate overlay system
- File preview image height uses `CGImageSource` header-only aspect ratio (no full decode)
- Window glass tint: `tintedLiquidGlass` with 25% `DetailPaneSurfaceColor` (warm stone, theme-aware)
- Split view double-click-to-reset: detected inside `DragGesture.onEnded` (< 3pt translation, < 300ms gap)
- Callout height: measured via `NSCell.cellSize(forBounds:)`, never `boundingRect`
- URL detection: `NSDataDetector` only, never regex
- Blockquote style: `headIndent = 20`, `tailIndent = -4`, `lineBreakMode = .byWordWrapping`

## Rich Text Serialization (TodoRichTextEditor)

Tag syntax: `[[b]]`, `[[i]]`, `[[u]]`, `[[s]]`, `[[h1-3]]`, `[[align:X]]`, `[[color|hex]]`, `[x]`/`[ ]`, `[[image|||]]`, `[[webclip|...]]`, `[[linkcard|title|desc|url]]`, `[[file|type|stored|original|viewMode]]`, `[[link|...]]`

Nesting order: align > heading/bold/italic > underline > strikethrough > color

## Sidebar Design Conventions

- `NoteListCard` `cornerRadius` default 12, override for concentric contexts (e.g. 8 inside pinned)
- Split containers: forced white bg + black text (theme-independent by design)
- All sidebar note rows: `.frame(height: 34)`
- `sidebarMenuItem` supports optional `shortcut:` parameter for hover hints
- Typography scale (updated 2026-04-05): sidebar heading sizes 15‚Üí13, 13‚Üí12, 11 stays

## User Preferences

- Never `.clipped()` or `.clipShape()` on parent containers unless explicitly requested
- User has a second Mac (Apple Silicon, macOS 14) for compatibility testing
